---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import HashGenerator from '../components/HashGenerator.vue';
---
<Layout title="Hash Generator — MD5, SHA-1, SHA-256, SHA-512" description="Generate MD5, SHA-1, SHA-256, SHA-384, SHA-512 hashes. 100% client-side." wide>
<h1>🔒 Hash Generator</h1>
<p>Generate cryptographic hashes: MD5, SHA-1, SHA-256, SHA-384, SHA-512. All client-side.</p>
<HashGenerator client:load />
<h2>💡 Use Cases</h2>
<ul><li><b>SHA-256</b> — Password hashing, file integrity</li><li><b>MD5</b> — Checksums, quick comparison (not for security)</li></ul>
<h2>❓ FAQ</h2>
<h3>Is my data sent anywhere?</h3><p>No. Uses the Web Crypto API in your browser.</p>
</Layout>
